### Q1 最基本测试
select second('2018-3-26 14:00:06.999') as x,second('2017-2-29 14:10:56.999') as y ,second(null) as z from dual;
+------+------+------+
| x    | y    | z    |
+------+------+------+
|    6 | NULL | NULL |
+------+------+------+
Warnings:
Warning	5086	Not timestamp Can not cast varchar value to timestamp type
select minute('2018-3-26 14:00:06.999') as x,minute('2017-2-29 14:10:56.999') as y ,minute(null) as z from dual;
+------+------+------+
| x    | y    | z    |
+------+------+------+
|    0 | NULL | NULL |
+------+------+------+
Warnings:
Warning	5086	Not timestamp Can not cast varchar value to timestamp type
