### Q3 复杂一点的测例
select * from func_t1 where second(c1) + minute(c2) = time_to_sec(c3) - to_seconds(c5) + length(c4) + 63695255698;
+---------------------+------------+----------------------------+-------------------+----------+
| c1                  | c2         | c3                         | c4                | c5       |
+---------------------+------------+----------------------------+-------------------+----------+
| 2018-06-04 09:24:00 | 2018-06-04 | 2018-06-04 09:24:45.432000 | 2018-2-27 6:01:59 | 20180604 |
+---------------------+------------+----------------------------+-------------------+----------+

